---
title: Cheesy Chicken & Creamy Spinach Sauce with Roasted Potato & Garlic Veggies
description: We've turbo-charged your chicken tonight! Special additions like a too-good-to-be-true cheesy and creamy spinach sauce,
herbed spices on the golden chunks of potato and a robust side of veggies are what it's all about. Happy days indeed!
